data.description: Highest and Best by Noon Thursday 4/18 Peace and Tranquility surrounds you at this beautiful home where you can enjoy views of Barton Lake everyday. In the evening time you can enjoy your favorite drink on your covered deck overlooking a wonderful park like setting. On Weekends you can drop your kayaks at the public boat launch which is a short 15 min walk or 3 min drive. This home has been beautifully updated and loved for by their owners and now they would love to pass it on to the next owners to create more amazing lake memories.
